<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="composition-n">composition <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌkɒmpə'zɪʃn/    美 /ˌkɑːmpə'zɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1u">1.<strong>[U] 组成；构成：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the chemical composition of the soil 
土壤的化学成分</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 创作；作曲；写作：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is good at the composition of short stories.
他擅长写短篇小说。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 作文；乐曲；作品：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a composition for the piano
钢琴曲</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is writing a composition. 
